    "Human-human-perceived-as-AI interaction.",
    "The responses in the first level were the same as those for the human-AI and human-human interactions.",
    "The second level was the same as that in the human-human interaction.",
    "For level 3, participants performed the exact same procedure as in the human-AI interaction.",
    "The only difference was that, while they were led to believe that they \"will be presented with the response of an AI algorithm that was trained to perform the task\", they were in fact interacting with the human participants from level 2."
